==Description==

The [[Image_Scaling|Image Scaling]] tool scales an image that was imported with the [[Image_CreateImagePlane|Image CreateImagePlane]] tool.

== Usage ==

# Press the {{Button|[[Image:Image_Scaling.svg|16px]] [[Image_Scaling|Image Scaling]]}} button.
# Click a first point on the 3D view.
# Click a second point on the 3D view.
# Select an existing image plane from the Model tree, created with the {{Button|[[Image:Image_CreateImagePlane.svg|16px]] [[Image_CreateImagePlane|Image CreateImagePlane]]}} tool.
# Add a distance in millimeters and press {{Button|OK}}.


